Tables of evolutionary tracks are only available in electronic form at
the {CDS} via anonymous ftp to cdsarc.u-strasbg.fr (130.79.128.5) or via
{http://cdsweb.u-strasbg.fr/cgi-bin/qcat?J/A+A/484/815}},
	journal = {Astronomy and Astrophysics},
	author = {G. Bertelli and L. Girardi and P. Marigo and E. Nasi},
