assumptions, we conclude that {{OMEGA}\_0\_} {\textasciitilde} 0.2- 0.5 and h {\textasciitilde} 0.7 {CDM} 
models with/without the cosmological constant reproduce simultaneously 
the observed temperature and luminosity functions of X-ray clusters at 
